summary: Virtual provides — foo-ng satisfies foo requirement
description: |
  System repo: foo-1.4, bar (baseline)
  Pre-installed: foo-ng-1.4 (Provides: foo, Obsoletes: foo < 3.0-1)
  Artifacts: None

  foo-ng satisfies the foo requirement via virtual provides.
  The presence check must use --whatprovides so that foo-ng is recognised.
  Installing bar must not disturb foo-ng.

environment+:
  EXPECTED_PACKAGE: foo-ng-1.4
  PRE_INSTALLED_PACKAGE: rpms/foo-ng-1.4/foo-ng-1.4*.rpm

/only-foo:
  summary+: " (only foo requested)"

/with-bar:
  summary+: " (foo and bar requested)"
  context+:
    with_bar: "true"
  environment+:
    SYSTEM_PACKAGE+: " bar"
